dct_title_s: Neighborhood Strategic Planning Areas Milwaukee, Wisconsin 2018
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents Neighborhood Strategic Planning (NSP) Areas for the City of Milwaukee in 2018. The dataset was originally published by the City of Milwaukee Information and Technology Management Division-GIS Section and the City of Milwaukee Community Development Grants Administration on June 17, 2019.[polygons representing NSP areas]
